+    **LOCATION:** §5.2–5.3: “moved … the median from about 205,000 to 201,923”; “roughly 98,000 to 87,000”; “roughly 70,000”; “tripled … to roughly 205,000”; “eleven public revision rounds”; “none was caught by the author unaided.”  
